Package net.smartcosmos.model.base

Foundational interfaces from which the entire SMART COSMOS object model is derived.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IAccountContext
    Establishes an account context that formally owns the domain resource.
    IAccountDomainResource<T>
    Account scoped domain resource.
    IDomainResource<T>
    Internal interface not suitable for public use.
    IMinimalReferentialObject  
    IMoniker
    Arbitrary textual field that is guaranteed to never be directly interpreted by the platform.
    INamedObject<T>
    Provides a human readable name and optional descriptive narrative.
    IReferentialObject
    Defines an explicit relationship between two otherwise disparate domain resources within the same account context.
    ITypedObject
    Establishes an ontological set of categories within a collection of peer domain resources.
    IUrnNamespace
    Sole means of uniquely identifying a specific object in the SMART COSMOS platform.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    EntityReferenceType
    Represents a specific type of platform entity in a generic operation.
